OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,FPainting London's roofs white or
OL,7,Freflective colours could save hundreds
OL,8,Fof lives in increasingly hot summers,
OL,9,Fa study has suggested.
OL,11,FCovering the capital's roofs in solar
OL,12,Fpanels could also have a positive -
OL,13,Falbeit smaller - impact in reducing
OL,14,Fheat-related deaths, while also
OL,15,Fgenerating large amounts of clean
OL,16,Fenergy for the city, the research
OL,17,Fshows.
