OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,FResearchers at University College
OL,7,FLondon (UCL) and the University of
OL,8,FExeter used computer modelling to
OL,9,Fanalyse the impact of "cool roofs" -
OL,10,Fpainted white or reflective colours -
OL,11,Fon temperatures in London during its
OL,12,Fwarmest ever summer in 2018.
OL,14,FThese light-coloured roofs, commonly
OL,15,Ffound in hot countries, absorb less
OL,16,Fradiant energy from the sun than
OL,17,Ftraditional dark roofs.
