OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,FThis helps counter some of the "urban
OL,7,Fheat island" effect which sees cities
OL,8,Fabsorbing a lot of heat and becoming
OL,9,Fwarmer than surrounding areas.
OL,11,FThe researchers examined their cooling
OL,12,Feffects in summer 2018, when there
OL,13,Fwere an estimated 786 deaths in
OL,14,FGreater London in June, July and
OL,15,FAugust attributable to the heat, as
OL,16,Ftemperatures averaged around 19.2C, or
OL,17,F1.6C above average for the time of
OL,18,Fyear.
