OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,FThey found that if all London's
OL,7,Frooftops were cool roofs it would
OL,8,Flower average outside air temperatures
OL,9,Fby 0.8C, and if all of them were
OL,10,Fcovered in solar photovoltaic (PV)
OL,11,Fpanels, which absorb some of the heat
OL,12,Fto convert to electricity,
OL,13,Ftemperatures would be down 0.3C.
OL,15,FThey estimated that 249 deaths could
OL,16,Fhave been avoided with full coverage
OL,17,Fof cool roofs, around a third of those
OL,18,Fwho died from the heat in 2018.
