OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,FAnd if all roofs carried solar panels,
OL,7,F96 deaths could have been avoided, and
OL,8,Fthe solar PV could generate up to 20
OL,9,Fterawatt hours of electricity, more
OL,10,Fthan half of the total London used in
OL,11,Fthe whole of 2018.
OL,13,FThe lives saved by the cool roofs
OL,14,Fwould have reduced the city's economic
OL,15,Fburden by around #615 million, and
OL,16,Fthose saved by the solar PV would have
OL,17,Freduced it by around #237 million, the
OL,18,Fresearchers said.
