OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,FThey also said that if 2% of buildings
OL,7,Fhad solar PV and the rest were cool
OL,8,Froofs it would have saved 248 lives
OL,9,Fand generated up to _146 million worth
OL,10,Fof clean electricity.
OL,12,FLead author Dr Charles Simpson, from
OL,13,FUCL, said: "If widely adopted, cool
OL,14,Froofs can significantly reduce the
OL,15,Fground-level air temperature of a city.
OL,17,F"The resulting cooling effect across
OL,18,Fthe city would save lives and improve
OL,19,Fthe quality of life for residents
OL,20,Fthroughout the urban area."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
