OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,FHe added: "Solar panels have great
OL,7,Fbenefits as a source of renewable
OL,8,Fpower, so it's good to see they won't
OL,9,Fmake the city hotter."
OL,11,FCo-author Professor Tim Taylor, of the
OL,12,FUniversity of Exeter, said: "The need
OL,13,Ffor our cities to adapt to climate
OL,14,Fchange is clear.
OL,16,F"Changing our roof spaces offers one
OL,17,Fpotential solution.
