OL,3,CWhy painting roofs white might have
OL,4,Csaved lives in London's hottest summer
OL,6,F"We need to encourage action like
OL,7,Fthis, to reduce the burden of excess
OL,8,Fheat on people living in urban areas
OL,9,Fand capture potential co-benefits,
OL,10,Fincluding energy generation."
OL,12,F- The study is published in the
OL,13,Fjournal Nature Cities.
